            <div class="section">
                <h2><span class="icon">üíª</span>Technical Achievements</h2>
                
                <h3>üî® Major Fixes Implemented</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>CS0101 Duplicate Types:</strong> Removed duplicate AddonManagement, used authoritative ManagementTools</li>
                    <li><strong>CS0116 Global Using:</strong> Replaced with Unity 2021.3 compatible using statements</li>
                    <li><strong>CS1061 Missing Properties:</strong> Fixed Player API calls (invisible, health, mana access patterns)</li>
                    <li><strong>CS0029 Type Conversions:</strong> Proper Health/Experience struct usage, long to int casts</li>
                    <li><strong>CS0103 Missing Methods:</strong> Implemented GetRarityMultiplier, GetBaseStat, movement fixes</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>üéØ System Enhancements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>uMMORPG Integration:</strong> Proper Player, Skills, Traits API usage</li>
                    <li><strong>Unity 2021.3 Compatibility:</strong> TextMeshPro enums, UI component access</li>
                    <li><strong>Movement System:</strong> Replaced direct agent access with Movement component</li>
                    <li><strong>Type Safety:</strong> Proper struct access patterns for Health/Experience</li>
                    <li><strong>Extension Methods:</strong> Clean player property access helpers</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

